title: SWE: Relationship Resolutions
itunes:title: SWE: Relationship Resolutions
itunes:subtitle: Free Friday: Emily and Menace want you to fly them to Vegas, women love talking on the phone, sober parties, everyone wants a threesome, one size fits most penises, Taco Bell aphrodisiac, can men and women really be friends?
description:
